reviews.text: Restaurant does not have sanitary operating toilets for public use. Signs directing customers to the washroom, leads to an outside corridor and then to washrooms. TWO out of the THREE toilets did not have toilet seats. How are guests supposed to use the toilet? The outdoor corridor to the washroom also smelled of sewage and is unsanitary by mcdonalds standards.
Good place to get the food quickely with less price. Also, one of the main sources to survive foreigners and middle class people in Hong Kong.
Standard McDonald's, bit shabby, but currently being revamped. If what you want is a McDonald's, it's perfectly acceptable.
One of the best McDonald's for drivers, as they have parking right outside the shop.  Good place for before or after joy ride #ParkingInSight

Bit of a language barrier as i am indian and my native language is hindi but i am fluent in english still the staff member requested me to point at my order on the menu card rather than get it straight away...bit annoying but the food was good.

result.name: 麥當勞

reviews.text: 最近廁所裝修完 晚上11點之後 至早上 大門上鎖 包括男女厠傷殘廁所 極不方便 食嘢唔可以去廁所唔知乜嘢 道理. 5月30號去過一次最近重新裝修 但洗手間夜晚上11時鎖上 唔知可唔可以去食環署投訴因為 食肆 規定要有廁所畀客人用,
一般麥常勞的水準、洗手間注意改善……
清潔一般，等食物時間很長
食物都是一般麥當勞質數，但職員就完全系醒目機靈，令客人感到非常舒服，又會幫助客人解決食物問題，值得嘗試。
